=\"skeptics1\"/>|| [[Simon Singh]], [[James Randi]], Paul Willis, [[Brian Dunning (skeptic)|Brian Dunning]], Krissy Wilson, [[Kylie Sturgess]], [[Pamela Gay]], [[The Skeptics' Guide to the Universe|SGU team]], [[George Hrab]], Era Segev, [[Richard Saunders (skeptic)|Richard Saunders]], [[Karl Kruszelnicki]], John Smyrk, Jules Morrow, Dick Smith, Steve Canenne, Simon Taylor, [[Rob Morrison (scientist)|Rob Morrison]], [[Eugenie Scott]], [[Fred Watson]] and [[Rachael Dunlop]] || 600+<ref name=\"SkepticOZ\">{{cite web|title=Amaz!ng|url=http://www.skeptics.com.au/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/theskeptic/2010/5.pdf|publisher=Skeptic|accessdate=September 2, 2011}}{{dead link|date=July 2018 |bot=Allecher |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n|-\n| July 14\u201317, 2011 || [[Southpoint Casino]], Enterprise, NV || TAM 9 From Outer Space || (Keynote) [[Neil DeGrasse Tyson]], [[Bill Nye]], [[Pamela Gay]], [[Lawrence Krauss]], [[Richard Dawkins]], [[Elizabeth Loftus]], [[Ben Radford]] and [[David Gorski]]||1650<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://archive.randi.org/site/index.php/component/content/article.html?id=246:amazng-meeting |title=Join us for The Amaz!ng Meeting 2012 |publisher=JREF |date=2012 |accessdate=October 25, 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161025115711/http://archive.randi.org/site/index.php/component/content/article.html?id=246:amazng-meeting |archivedate=October 25, 2016 }}</ref>\n|-\n|July 12\u201315, 2012 || [[Southpoint Casino]], Enterprise, NV ||TAM 2012 Skepticism and the Future<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.amazingmeeting.com/TAM2012/ |title=The Amazing Meeting 2012 |publisher=randi.org |accessdate=July 4, 2012 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120707142018/http://www.amazingmeeting.com/TAM2012/ |archivedate=July 7, 2012 }}</ref>\n|[[Deirdre Barrett]], [[The Skeptics' Guide to the Universe|SGU's]] Evan Bernstein, Bob Novella and Jay Novella; [[Eugenie Scott]], Robert Blaskiewicz, [[Bryan & Baxter]], [[Kelly Carlin]],